          <li class=\"project__list-item\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>SPD事業（院内物流システム）</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"project__card\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n        <div class=\"project__icon\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n          <figure data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n            <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/service-icon.svg\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n          </figure>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"project__body\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n          <div class=\"project__inner\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n            <h3 class=\"project__title\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>サービス</h3>\n            <div class=\"project__textarea\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n              <p class=\"project__text\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>医療機器業界において各医療機関と100年以上のお付き合いをさせていただいた中で得た、様々なノウハウを蓄積しています。</p>\n              <ul class=\"project__list\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>\n                <li class=\"project__list-item\" data-astro-cid-xxz2ihco>コンサルティングサービス</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <section id=\"department\">\n      <div class=\"main-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"main-inner\">\n          <h2 class=\"heading2\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>\n  <b class=\"heading2__lead\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>Department</b>\n  <span class=\"heading2__title\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>職種について</span>\n</h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"department\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n  <div id=\"interview01\" class=\"department__unit\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n          <div class=\"department__wrap\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n            <div class=\"department__intro\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n              <div class=\"department__heading\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n                <b class=\"department__title\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>営業職</b>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"department__img\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n                <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/department01.jpg\" width=\"754.5\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\">\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n        \n            <div class=\"department__textarea\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n              <h3 class=\"heading3\" data-astro-cid-lqilmf5p>医療機関の<br>「第一相談窓口」を目指す</h3>\n              <p class=\"department__text\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>顧客密着型のルートセールスが基本で、担当となった医療機関へメーカー営業担当と協力しながら商品提案を行います。</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      \n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n          <div class=\"department__point\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n            <h4 class=\"department__point-title\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>Point</h4>\n            <ul class=\"department__list\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n              <li class=\"department__list-item\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>研修や実務を通して学ぶ為、医療知識はゼロからスタートでOK</li><li class=\"department__list-item\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>幅広い医療分野の知識が身に付く</li><li class=\"department__list-item\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>医師・看護師・検査技師・事務など様々な医療従事者と日々関わる</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      \n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n          <div class=\"department__button\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n            <a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/persons/interview01.html\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>営業職のC.Sを見る</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a><a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/persons/interview02.html\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>営業職のH.Mを見る</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div id=\"interview03\" class=\"department__unit\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n          <div class=\"department__wrap\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n            <div class=\"department__intro\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n              <div class=\"department__heading\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n                <b class=\"department__title\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>技術職</b>\n              </div>\n              <figure class=\"department__img\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n                <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/department02.jpg\" width=\"754.5\" height=\"450\" alt=\"\">\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n        \n            <div class=\"department__textarea\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n              <h3 class=\"heading3\" data-astro-cid-lqilmf5p>技術を磨き続けて<br>修理･メンテナンスの<wbr>プロを目指す</h3>\n              <p class=\"department__text\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>多種多様な医療機器の修理・メンテナンスを担当。出張修理、社内修理、院内常駐など業務内容に応じた働き方となります。</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      \n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n          <div class=\"department__point\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n            <h4 class=\"department__point-title\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>Point</h4>\n            <ul class=\"department__list\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n              <li class=\"department__list-item\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>メーカー修理技術者講習を受けての実務</li><li class=\"department__list-item\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>株式会社ムトウに籍を置き、グループ会社３社のいずれかにて活躍</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      \n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n          <div class=\"department__button\" data-astro-cid-4ihtarta>\n            <a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/persons/interview03.html\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>技術職のO.Sを見る</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </d